commit dabf32a5ad706726412ba5c64e1ea614a707b928
Author: Behdad Esfahbod <behdad@behdad.org>
Date:   Tue Feb 23 15:38:43 2016 +0900

    1.2.1

 NEWS         | 13 +++++++++++++
