commit affacf2f37db767ab8df7f2db6cd9e0e9b0a2b8a
Author: Behdad Esfahbod <behdad@behdad.org>
Date:   Sun Dec 28 16:20:31 2014 -0800

    [ft] Open blob in READONLY mode

