commit af1aa362cacc652ab8ffda05a5d98a3ff5430439
Author: Behdad Esfahbod <behdad@behdad.org>
Date:   Fri Mar 14 15:52:47 2014 -0700

    If HAVE_ICU_BUILTIN is defined, use hb-icu Unicode callbacks

