commit e6f7479fe34fb4a7cada61d84c2ed70d1fd565c8
Author: Behdad Esfahbod <behdad@behdad.org>
Date:   Sat Jul 28 18:34:58 2012 -0400

    [GSUB] Simplify would-apply

