    SINHALA: 271715 out of 271847 tests passed. 132 failed (0.0485567%)
    TAMIL: 1091837 out of 1091837 tests passed. 0 failed (0%)
    TELUGU: 970550 out of 970573 tests passed. 23 failed (0.00236973%)

