commit 0db299ccad346d9ea5573ea8408b78d9997bd379
Author: Behdad Esfahbod <behdad@behdad.org>
Date:   Thu May 20 13:30:09 2010 +0100

    Change hb_feature_t to keep tag/int instead of string

